  <brief_title>Effect of BNP (Brain Natriuretic Peptides) on Endothelial Dysfunction Induced by Coronary Angioplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4 Study of Patients Receiving BNP or NTG (IV) During Angioplasty, Re-examined 24 Hours Later Using the Flow-mediated Brachial Artery Dilation Study, and Blood Assays for Pro BNP and ET1</official_title>
  <sponsors>
